"metaSummary_en": "Mega Altaria ex Espeon is still by far the most played deck (7.58% usage) but caps at 50.67% win rate; the best genuinely playable win rate belongs to Suicune ex Baxcalibur (52.08%), ahead of Mega Altaria ex Gourgeist (51.69%). The meta is very stable, dominated by Mega decks and Magnezone/Miraidon variants. Official news: the Everyday Wonders mini-expansion launches Monday June 29 at 6:00 p.m. PDT, starring Pikachu, Piplup, Snorlax, Greedent and Sylveon (Mega Diancie ex as the chase card), with backdrops and covers from June 30. July brings the Everyday Wonders Emblem Event, Community Week and the Hisuian Zorua Drop Event. Next major expansion: Ruler of the Skies (~July 30, Mega Rayquaza ex).",
